parameters:
Zerachiel: Let's go on an adventure to
the Magic Continent!

Zerachiel: I've been cooped up on the
ship for two weeks, so my body was
starting to get stiff.

Zerachiel: Well then... I guess we
should head to the magical city of Vaal.

Zerachiel: I wonder if I should ask the
residents how to get to the magical city
of Vaal?

Let's gather information about the
magical city of Vaal.

Girl: This is Minato Ward. If you go
north, there's a tavern.

Old Man: There are many travelers this
year, huh.

Old Man: Earlier, a group of three young
adventurers came and asked about the way
to the magical city of Vaal.

Old Man: Would you like to have some
tea?

Old Man: Would you like to have some
tea?

Old Man: Would you like to have some
tea?

Old Man: Would you like to have some
tea?

Old Man: Would you like to have some
tea?

Old Man: ...I hear that the war is
starting.

Old Man: Many lives will be lost again.
But that's how the world works, isn't
it?

Old Man: I wonder who will survive in
the end.

Old Man: Would you like to have some
tea?

Zerachiel: The tea was delicious, wasn't
it.

Effy: You seemed to be having fun,
Grandpa.
